							Projects
						</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
							Browse my technical projects and experiments
						</p>
					</a>
					
					<a href="/about" class="group block p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:border-primary-300 dark:hover:border-primary-600 transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg">
